
Action: file_editor create /app/memory/PRD.md --file-text "# AstraAi — PRD

## Original Problem Statement
> \"Fai un Ai si chiamerà AstraAi non dirmi più nulla fai tutto da solo\"
> (Italian) — Build an AI; it will be called AstraAi; don't ask me anything else, do everything on your own.

## Defaults chosen (no user clarification available)
- **App type**: AI chatbot (ChatGPT-like SPA)
- **LLM**: OpenAI **gpt-5.2** via `emergentintegrations` + `EMERGENT_LLM_KEY`
- **Auth**: none (MVP)
- **Storage**: MongoDB (`astra_sessions`, `astra_messages` collections)
- **Language**: UI in Italian
- **Theme**: celestial/editorial dark theme (Playfair Display + Outfit, starlight-amber accents on deep space #05070A)

## Architecture
- **Backend** (FastAPI, `/app/backend/server.py`)
  - `GET /api/` — health
  - `POST /api/sessions` — create session
  - `GET /api/sessions` — list (sorted by `updated_at` desc)
  - `GET /api/sessions/{id}/messages` — chronological messages
  - `DELETE /api/sessions/{id}` — delete session + messages
  - `POST /api/chat` — send a message; creates a session if none; persists user + assistant; replays prior turns for memory
- **Frontend** (React + React Router, Shadcn UI, Tailwind)
  - `/app/frontend/src/pages/ChatPage.jsx` — routes `/` and `/c/:sessionId`
  - `/app/frontend/src/components/astra/{Sidebar,MessageBubble,EmptyState,ChatInput}.jsx`
  - `/app/frontend/src/lib/api.js` — axios client using `REACT_APP_BACKEND_URL`

## User Personas
- Italian-speaking user wanting a premium, fast, focused AI chat.

## What's been implemented (2026-02)
- End-to-end chat with GPT-5.2 (multi-turn memory verified: \"Marco\" recalled).
- Session list in sidebar (new chat, select, delete with confirmation dialog).
- Empty state with 4 suggestion cards; typing indicator; mobile responsive sidebar.
- Italian UI, celestial dark theme, Playfair Display + Outfit fonts.
- Full test suite: 9/9 backend pytest passing, frontend Playwright e2e passing.

## Backlog / Next
- **P1**: Streaming responses (SSE) for a more fluid chat.
- **P1**: Markdown rendering (lists, code blocks, bold) in assistant messages.
- **P2**: Rename a conversation (inline edit on sidebar item).
- **P2**: Copy message / regenerate response buttons.
- **P2**: Light/Dark toggle.
- **P2**: Optional auth (Emergent Google Auth) for per-user sessions.
- **P3**: Native LlmChat history replay (role-based) instead of concatenated prompt to reduce tokens on long chats.
- **P3**: Migrate `@app.on_event('shutdown')` to FastAPI lifespan.
"
